\id 2JN
\ide  UTF-8
\h 2 Yohani 
\toc1 2 Yohani 
\toc2 2 Yohani 
\toc3 2jn 
\mt1 2 Yohani  
\c 1
\cl Undyango 1 
\p
\v 1 Unuhuma hugogolo uhuluta nuvadala avasayiwe na vana vavene vavo nevaganile katiha uvolweli sio umwe netu bali navoni avavihwelewa uvuyalweli.  
\v 2 Husababu yeyo yelegati mvenena yigona sana ipaha humwisio.  
\v 3 Ukuhungu nu huhovaka chale nufwe uhuhuma hwangulove na hwa swambe Uyesu avana va Daada vale nulugano.  
\v 4 Naho wihe sana navile nigundula baazi ya vana vavile viluta vunonu, vavile vipohela ululagelo hwa Daada.  
\v 5 Ululino ni huhudova, vedala, sio nihuhwa ndihela ululagilo ulupya, nayuve vidala yinogiwa uhuganana yufwe hwa yufwe. uvu vuvugane uvunigiwa tugendage nalwo.  
\v 6 Ulu lulagelo ulwutapoline uhuhuma pavutengulelo tutahiwa uhugenda nalwo.  
\v 7 Uhuva avadesivingi vahumile mkelunga savaeli we uhumwedena ava wotwita vadesi.  
\v 8 Mwelole mwevene amambo gago samwayalohe gala aga mwavombile.  
\v 9 Hela mnu endelele huvulongo ehuduma eyale nayo eya Kelesti.  
\v 10 Kama umunu ihwicha huliomwensileta amafundesio msite unupohela mnyumba namsite uhuponia.  
\v 11 Umnu uviponia iva alungine humbivi.  
\v 12 Nelenago amambo mingi aga huusimbila, sana nogwe uhasimbila mlikalatasi nu wino. Lakini ninogwa uhwi cha twa gane humiho, uhuta uhuhovosha hweto huve sawa.  
\v 13 Avana va naacha venyo wigane che vihuvaponia.   